OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779192669
OL,3,CTeen destroys memorial to young boys
OL,4,Cin a moment of 'sheer cruelty'
OL,6,FFootage has been released of the
OL,7,Fmoment a teenager destroys a memorial
OL,8,Fto two young boys who died in a crash,
OL,9,Fin what police describe as "a moment
OL,10,Fof 'sheer cruelty".
OL,12,FHeartfelt letters were placed among
OL,13,Fhundreds of pounds worth of flowers in
OL,14,Fa tribute to Mason Renhard, 17, and
OL,15,FDamien Dean, 16.
OL,17,FThe teenagers both died when their car
OL,18,Fhit with a tree off Corhampton Lane in
OL,19,FJuly 2025.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/6
