PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779192669
OL,3,CTeen destroys memorial to young boys
OL,4,Cin a moment of 'sheer cruelty'
OL,6,FRyan Edwards, 18, of Fox Close in
OL,7,FWarsash, was filmed kicking and
OL,8,Ftrampling the flowers, after claiming
OL,9,Fhe was angry with Mason over an
OL,10,Funrelated matter.
OL,12,FReacting to the act of vandalism,
OL,13,FMason's family said: "Nothing in this
OL,14,Fworld compares to the pain of losing a
OL,15,Fchild.
OL,17,F"Since the day Mason died in that
OL,18,Fhorrific crash with Damo, our lives
OL,19,Fhave been consumed by grief ` raw,
OL,20,Frelentless, and overwhelming.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779192669
OL,3,CTeen destroys memorial to young boys
OL,4,Cin a moment of 'sheer cruelty'
OL,6,F"Every morning we wake up and remember
OL,7,Fall over again that he is gone. There
OL,8,Fis no break from the pain. No escape.
OL,10,F"We are parents living with a wound
OL,11,Fthat will never heal.
OL,13,F"In the middle of that unbearable
OL,14,Fgrief, we placed flowers, tributes,
OL,15,Fand messages of love at the site where
OL,16,Four boy lost his life. That memorial
OL,17,Fbecame the only place we could go to
OL,18,Ffeel close to Mason ` to talk to him,
OL,19,Fto cry for him, to try to make since
OL,20,Fof a reality that will never make
OL,21,Fsense.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779192669
OL,3,CTeen destroys memorial to young boys
OL,4,Cin a moment of 'sheer cruelty'
OL,6,F"Those flowers were the only way we
OL,7,Fhad left to honour our child, and then
OL,8,FRyan took it upon himself to destroy
OL,9,Fthem.
OL,11,F"He didn't just damage a few items. He
OL,12,Fdestroyed hundreds of pounds worth of
OL,13,Fmemorial flowers and tributes `
OL,14,Fsymbols of love, heartbreak and
OL,15,Fmemory. He shattered the only fragile
OL,16,Fpeace we had managed to build.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779192669
OL,3,CTeen destroys memorial to young boys
OL,4,Cin a moment of 'sheer cruelty'
OL,6,F"We were already living every parent's
OL,7,Fworst nightmare, and Ryan chose to
OL,8,Fmake it worse. He made a conscious
OL,9,Fdecision to add trauma to parents who
OL,10,Fwere already broken.
OL,12,F"If he ever becomes a parent, and if
OL,13,Fhe ever loves a child the way we love
OL,14,FMason, perhaps then he will realise
OL,15,Fthe sheer cruelty of what he did. And
OL,16,Fmaybe, when he looks at his record, he
OL,17,Fwill finally feel the shame he should
OL,18,Fhave felt the moment he touched those
OL,19,Fflowers."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/6
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
