CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1779192669
OL,3,CTeen destroys memorial to young boys
OL,4,Cin a moment of 'sheer cruelty'
OL,6,FEdwards was ordered to carry out 300
OL,7,Fhours of unpaid work and pay #350
OL,8,Fcompensation to each family for what
OL,9,Fthe magistrate described as a
OL,10,F"sickening and serious situation" and
OL,11,Fthe "stress and turmoil he has caused
OL,12,Fas a result of his actions".
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/6
